<%= form_for(@form, class: 'needs-validation') do |f| %>
  <h1>Graphics Arts Loan Collection (GALC) - Borrowing Contract</h1>

  <%= render 'application/form_error', model: @form if @form.errors.any? %>

  <br />

  <p>Borrowers must be in good standing (no fines, no overdue items, and no blocks) in order to borrow a print from the Graphic Arts Loan Collection at the Morrison Library.</p>

  <h2>Borrowing Guidelines</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>The current academic year GALC Borrowing Agreement form must be signed electronically by clicking the Agree button below prior to checking out a print.</li>
    <li>Borrowers may check-out up to two prints each academic year beginning with the Fall semester.</li>
    <li>Prints are due a few weeks before the Spring semester ends. The GALC prints do not circulate during the Summer.</li>
    <li>Prints are the property of the University of California.</li>
    <li>You are personally responsible for the prints. You must check out and return them yourself to the Morrison Library during open hours.</li>
    <li>Borrowers may not loan or transfer prints to another person.</li>
    <li>Prints must be returned within two weeks if you withdraw from the university or otherwise lose your university status.</li>
		<li>Prints must be returned if you leave the university for more than two weeks outside of the winter break.</li>
    <li>Prints must not be removed from the frame for any reason.</li>
    <li>Prints must not be copied.</li>
    <li>Prints must not be hung in a damp room or in direct sunlight.</li>
    <li>Clean only with a dry cloth.</li>
</ul>


  <div class="form-check required">
    <%= f.check_box :borrow_check, {class: 'form-check-input', required: true}, "checked", "unchecked" %>
    <%= f.label :borrow_check, "I agree", {class: 'form-check-label'} %>
  </div>

  <br />

  <h2>Fines and Liability</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You are fully responsible for the good care and safe return of a print.</li>
    <li>If a print or frame is damaged in any way, return it immediately to the Morrison Library.</li>
    <li>If a print is damaged, you will be billed for repair costs and processing fees. If a print is damaged beyond repair, you will be billed the value of the print plus frame, which could exceed $1,000.</li>
    <li>Prints not returned by the due date will result in a $100 fine.</li>
    <li>Prints overdue to the extent they reach a billed stage can result in a charge for the total value of the print plus frame, which could exceed $1,000.</li>
		<li>Prints not returned in the packing materials they were checked out in will be charged a $10 materials fee.</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="form-check required">
    <%= f.check_box :fine_check, {class: 'form-check-input', required: true}, "checked", "unchecked" %>
    <%= f.label :fine_check, "I agree", {class: 'form-check-label'} %>
  </div>

  <br />  

  <div class="btn-group" role="group">
    <%= f.submit(class: "btn btn-primary") %>
  </div>
<% end %>
